**More information:**
- Visit the [Hive Helsinki](https://www.hive.fi/en/about-hive). On the website, you'll find information about the school's mission, curriculum, admission process, and its unique peer-to-peer learning methodology. Hive Helsinki is part of the global 42 Network, offering an innovative education model with no teachers or formal classes, where students learn by completing projects.
- Visit the [global 42 Network](https://www.42network.org/). This site will provide insights into the global community of coding schools that follow the 42 educational model. The 42 Network spans multiple countries and focuses on project-based learning, fostering a collaborative environment where students teach and learn from each other. 